	<div class="forumopening">
		<p class="forumopening-title">
			<a href="/forum/can-technology-end-poverty">Opening<span>:</span></a>
		</p>
		<p class="forumopening-author">
			<a href="/author/kentaro-toyama">Kentaro Toyama</a>		</p>
		<div class="forumopening-content">
			<div class="forumopening-img" style="background-image:url(/sites/all/themes/br_hhog/assets/release/images/patterns_avatars/triangles1.png);">
				<a href="/forum/can-technology-end-poverty" class="forumopening-img-linkcover"></a>
			</div>
			<p class="forumopening-summary">
				<a href="/forum/can-technology-end-poverty">Many development experts promote information and communication technology (ICT) as a way to relieve global poverty. They should pay more attention to the human beings who use it.</a>
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
    </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
</div>			
